@startuml Registration_Flow
actor Customer
participant "React Frontend" as UI
participant "AuthController" as Auth
participant "CustomerService" as Service
database "MySQL" as DB

Customer -> UI: Click Register
Customer -> UI: Fill form (Name, Email, Password, etc.)
UI -> Auth: POST /api/auth/register (Customer Object)
Auth -> Service: register(customer)
Service -> DB: SELECT count(*) FROM customers WHERE email = ?
DB --> Service: 0 (No Dupont)
Service -> Service: Hash Password (BCrypt)
Service -> DB: INSERT INTO customers (...)
DB --> Service: Success
Service --> Auth: Success message
Auth --> UI: 200 OK "Đăng ký thành công"
UI -> Customer: Redirect to Login
@enduml
